				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Bone sculptures that Ketheric have built when turning to Myrkul during his containment in Thorm's mausoleum. Since he used material at hand some if not many of these are actually Thorm family members of the past generations.\n\nThis one looks like a dozen or so skulls connected together in a circle with bones like candles sticking from the top. "
